                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just an idea, here, also ...
<br />

<br />
Level 1: same
<br />
Level 2: pops out 3 copies of the player (possibly entertaining 3 mobs)
<br />
Level 3: the suggested fading memories effect
<br />

<br />
Then, as is pretty typical of our aa's and expansions add:
<br />

<br />
Hasten Doppleganger:  This ability lowers the re-use time of the blah, blah.
<br />

<br />
This would mimic what they've done with other abilities, and suck up even more aa's, so I think they might go for it.  At least, the second part ... the suggested changes to the first might be too useful, or neato, to be considered.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: violet">Sage Loriwen Tathrenlin</span></span>
