                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I agree that lvl 2 & 3 of Dopple certainly aren't worth the cost.  I think its been made pretty clear that a Fading Memories effect will not happen.  
<br />

<br />
The ideas I like best for increased levels are reduced reuse times (lvl 2 = 20mins lvl 3 = 10 mins), or additional dopplegangers (lvl 2 = 2 Mr. D, lvl 3 = 3 Mr. D). 
<br />

<br />
Since FM isn't going to happen (understandably in my opinion) I would like to see a boggle recourse on upgraded levels of Dopple (in addition to one of the above). 
<br />

<br />
Level 1 = same Mr. D pops with your hate + 1 (or similar smallish number)
<br />

<br />
Level 2 = Mr. D (or 2) pops with your current hate + 1, and you are dropped 500 pts (1 boggle) on Mobs hate list.
<br />

<br />
Level 3 = Mr. D (or 3) pops with your current hate + 1, and you are dropped 1000 pts (2 boggles) on Mobs hate list.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
