<br />

<br />
1. Charm, hasten, and give weapons to a nice baddy in an LDON.
<br />

<br />
2.  Watch your l33t dr00d pull 7 mobs, even though it requires going into two roos to do it.
<br />

<br />
3.  Send the pet in to attack and start locking the adds down while the cleric dies and the wizard evacs.
<br />

<br />
4.  On the way to recovering the cleric's body, charm your ex-pet.
<br />

<br />
5.  Watch as your pet goes tearing off after the mobs you pulled since it still has agro on them.
<br />

<br />
6.  Spam "Pet back off" as much as you can.
<br />

<br />
7.  (optional)  If you are close enough, sometimes the mobs themselves will come tearing after your pet when you charm it.  They will see your hapless cleric and kill him again of course.
<br />

<br />
