This has nothing to do with what I was talking about though.
<br />

<br />
This is your old pet still having those mobs on its hate list (and vice versa) so it wants to try to kill them (and them it) when you recharm it.   
<br />

<br />
That really has nothing to do with whether or not your pet hitting a mob is adding additional aggro -to- -you- for each bit of damage it does.   (I see no reason to believe that the aforementioned situation is the case, BTW).</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
