</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">This is mostly noticable when you try to sit, but can also be seen when you have a pet with insane dps. Also, seems to matter if you have any active agro on your own. If I haste/dual wield a heavy hitting pet in the mountain trials, for example, it can be hard to find a tank who can keep agro (off of me) if I'm also casting on the mobs (tash and slow). 
